    <!-- EN: When you press Accept, a crafter you’ve chosen will bring the resources onto the frame and begin
assembling a warcasket. The speed of the assembly depends on the crafting skill of your crafter.
Once the process is completed, a warcasket will leave the platform. Be careful, as the pawn
on the platform can still die of hunger when on the platform - you should prioritize the warcasket
assembly over other tasks. -->
  <VFEP.WarcasketText>当按下了“接受”选项后，你指定的组装者将会把所需资源带到铸造厂处以开始组装无畏战棺。组装的速度取决于铸造者的手工技能等级。\n组装完成后，新的无畏战棺将会离开铸造厂。请注意：进入铸造厂的殖民者仍然会感到饥饿——为了避免出现饿死事故，你应该优先完成无畏战棺的组装。</VFEP.WarcasketText>
